http interface:

get /tasks => list
get /tasks/:name => get
post /tasks/:name => set
delete /tasks/:name => del
get /tasks/:name/run => run
get /tasks/:name/history => history ? from, to


filesystem

/var/tasks/:name/:timestamp/state
/var/tasks/:name/:timestamp/stdout
/var/tasks/:name/:timestamp/stderr
/var/tasks/:name/current => link to current run


config

/etc/*.json
{
  'cron_schedule': "*/15 * * * *",
  'cmd': "echo 'peep'"
}


flow

get tasks
schedule => closest run
run => fort, dup2, exec, return code (!)
GOTO "get tasks"

